<span class="lbl">By stage</span>
<h2 class="h2">Right hire by company stage</h2>
<div class="table-wrap"><table class="t"><thead><tr><th>Stage</th><th>Most common right answer</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr><td>Pre-PMF / under $1M revenue</td><td>Neither, founder owns marketing</td></tr>
<tr><td>$1M-$3M revenue, no marketing leader</td><td>Fractional CMO + 1 marketing coordinator</td></tr>
<tr><td>$3M-$10M, no marketing leader</td><td>Fractional CMO; marketing director after 6-12 months</td></tr>
<tr><td>$3M-$10M, strategy clear, need execution</td><td>Marketing director</td></tr>
<tr><td>$10M-$25M, no senior marketing leader</td><td>Fractional CMO + marketing director (often together)</td></tr>
<tr><td>$25M-$50M</td><td>Full-time CMO + marketing director</td></tr>
<tr><td>$50M+</td><td>Full-time CMO + VP marketing or director(s)</td></tr>
</tbody></table></div>
</div></section>


